{
  "stem": "18813.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after they line us up, in the designated barracks for was, the barracks was just wood and rats from every corner.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, like myself, I'm scared of mouse, and I'm scared of rats.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I, I don't know from where I got the stick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So for as long I was in Auschwitz, I was sleeping like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody knew me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was doing that, so nothing would touch me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were not working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just one day they were caught-- some people who had to give blood for the German Army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was lucky enough, again, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will give blood because they were just taking blood as long-- as soon-- she fainted or whatever, he fainted.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They stopped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, but woman-- but they were-- I'm sorry, it was only women.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Auschwitz was all women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My husband went to Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To, to Brunnlitz?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] 350?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Could it be possible?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, and majority give blood-- a majority.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very few-- I had to clean the barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- they didn't know where they're going, where they are taking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when they came back-- so then you were lucky.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You, you didn't give blood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We all give blood.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- but the blood was good for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the Jews were no good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Jewish blood was good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They needed blood for the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They told us make us ready-- ready with whatever we had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had line-ups.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were taking-- how did we go to-- we-- you were asking me about leaving Auschwitz, yes?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Again by train, I think, but we were going-- we knew where we going, that Schindler is taking us out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really do not know.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
